companyName: Yong Bai Chao New Retail Corporation
description: Yong Bai Chao New Retail Corporation does not have significant operations. Previously, the company was involved in the development and sale of emission control devices for small spark ignition combustion engines. The company was formerly known as Environmental Control Corp. and changed its name to Yong Bai Chao New Retail Corporation in October 2021. Yong Bai Chao New Retail Corporation was founded in 1999 and is based in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
